    "summary": "The transcript features a teacher-persona user guiding the assistant through a discussion on substantive vs. procedural due process. The assistant consistently adopts a normative stance, framing substantive due process as a superior method for protecting rights and dismissing the counter-argument of judicial activism as a matter of necessary constitutional evolution.",
